      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まずは新婚生活のイメージでの撮影だな\nさくら、今日は大丈夫そうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're starting with shots about the newlywed life.\nSakura‚ are you feeling okay today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫も大丈夫、今の私に隙はありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m more than okay! I’m perfect right now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2836509704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.5970526059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に沢山練習してもらったので\n花嫁としての知識も一杯増えてますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to all the practice we did together‚\nI’ve learned a lot about being a bride!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.2694561958
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
