      "text": "{user}さんと寮の掃除をしたり\nサニピみんなのお弁当を作ったり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I cleaned the dorm with {user}-san‚\nmade lunch boxes for everyone in Sunny Peace‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0894660085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "絶品の卵焼きを作るために\nフライパンの素振りを千回くらいやったり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and to perfect my rolled omelet‚\nI practiced flipping the frying pan about a thousand times…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7691738331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "最後の特訓には心当たりないんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have no idea about the last one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1345352172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.1345352172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、私が思う花嫁力を鍛えるために\nいろいろやってきましたから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ to improve my skills as a bride‚\nI’ve done a lot of things!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.1183676878
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "今日の撮影には自信があります！\n今の私は世界一の花嫁ですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m confident about today’s shoot!\nI’m the best bride in the world right now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5998983541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "銀河一には届かなかったが\n自信があるのはいいことだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not the best in the galaxy‚ but\nit’s good to be confident.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.3523590246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、{user}さんとの練習で\n思ったこともあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And while practicing with you‚ {user}-san‚\nI realized something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんみたいな人と結婚したら\n楽しい結婚生活が送れるかもしれないな～、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I were to marry someone like you‚ {user}-san‚\nI think I’d have a fun married life~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.7137416678
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "あの時の気持ちを忘れずに挑めば\nいい撮影になるんじゃないかと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I don’t forget that feeling\nI think the shoot will go well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.7582087673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "役に立てたのなら何よりだ\n……お、そろそろ撮影の時間のようだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad I was able to help.\n…Oh‚ looks like it’s almost time for the shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.6333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　では、行ってきますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay! I’m off then!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6293656505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、頑張ってな。……それにしても、俺みたいな人と\nって、どういう意味だったんだ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ do your best. …But what did she mean by\n“someone like me”…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7333337148,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1725.919676199993,
          "startTime": 85.8666670482
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4200.000000000003,
          "startTime": 93.9333337148
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.4211779115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、さくら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5211784201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です！\nどうでしたか？　ちゃんと出来ていました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You worked hard!\nHow did I do? Was it okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.566664505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.8070714073
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ファンのみんながさくらとの結婚生活を\n想像出来る最高の写真が撮れていたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ the photos turned out great. The fans will be\nable to imagine a newlywed life with you‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2919836647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "次はいよいよウエディングドレスを着た撮影だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next up is finally the wedding dress shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6264362729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.3473206595
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　……この仕事を受けた時は\nただ着てみたいなって気持ちだけでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! …When I first accepted this job‚\nI just wanted to wear a wedding dress.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、いろんな練習をしたおかげか\n前よりもずっと、気持ちが強くなっちゃってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But after doing all that practice‚\nmy feelings have grown much stronger.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.0958463743
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "ウエディングドレスに袖を通した私を想像したら\nまだ着てもいないのに感動してきちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just imagining myself wearing a wedding dress\nmakes me emotional‚ even before putting it on…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "早くこの気持ちを、見てくれる人達にも伝えたい\nだから、私……頑張ってきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to convey this feeling to everyone who sees it.\nSo… I’m going to do my best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "私、あなたと結婚出来るこの日を\nずっと待っていたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been waiting for this day‚\nthe day I can marry you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.0000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_03-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "あなただけの、特別な存在になって\nこれからの人生を、一緒に歩いていく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll be your special someone‚\nand we’ll walk through life together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.0666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
